name: Fourteenth General Swedish Farming Meeting in Norrköping
obverse: Bust of Oscar II facing right.
obverse_inscriptions: OSCAR II SVERIGES OCH NORRIGES KONUNG
reverse_inscriptions: BELÖNINGSMEDALJ VID FJORTONDE ALLMÄNNA SVENSKA LANDTBRUKSMÖTET I NORRKÖPING 1876.
description: This medal was made to commemorate the Fourteenth General Swedish Farming Meeting in Norrköping on July 25, 1876.
